1
00:00:00,350 --> 00:00:04,060
The plans you refer to will soon be back
in our hands.

2
00:00:04,094 --> 00:00:07,960
Any attack made by the rebels against this
station would be a useless gesture.

3
00:00:08,260 --> 00:00:11,064
No matter what technical
data they've obtained, this

4
00:00:11,065 --> 00:00:13,740
station is now the ultimate
power in the universe.

5
00:00:14,800 --> 00:00:16,400
I suggest we use it.

6
00:00:16,760 --> 00:00:20,520
Don't be too proud of this technological
terror you've constructed.

7
00:00:20,900 --> 00:00:25,800
The ability to destroy a planet is
insignificant next to the power of the Force.

8
00:00:26,459 --> 00:00:30,000
Don't try to frighten us with your
sorcerer's ways, Lord Vader.

9
00:00:30,300 --> 00:00:32,631
Your sad devotion to
that ancient religion has

10
00:00:32,632 --> 00:00:35,721
not helped you conjure
up the stolen data tapes.

11
00:00:35,780 --> 00:00:39,280
Or given you clairvoyance enough to find
the rebels' hidden fortress.

12
00:00:46,410 --> 00:00:48,890
I find your lack of faith disturbing.

13
00:00:50,490 --> 00:00:51,490
Enough of this.

14
00:00:51,650 --> 00:00:52,870
Vader, release him.

15
00:00:53,430 --> 00:00:54,470
As you wish.

